&lt;p&gt;Please book&nbsp;by email&nbsp;at&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:kimyou84@elbon.co.kr&quot;&gt;kimyou84@elbon.co.kr&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;or contact ELBON the table by phone at +82-2-547-4100&lt;/p&gt;
